Maintainer: Varun Ravi <varsi146@student.liu.se>
Description: Retrieves data by constructing a URL query based on a base URL defined in the
    function and then converts the JSON data from the Kolada API into a tibble data frame and 
    returns it which is then used in a shiny application for visualization.
